summary: A cheat to gives vampiric invisibility, muffle and fortify sneak for 3min. I use this for testing and just thought I'd offer it. I didn't see another spell like it.
descriptionHtml:
I got tired of being spotted when trying out some of the weapon mods I was trying to create so created this 'cheat' spell. However, once you 'use' something, you are visible again, but you can
use it in combat so...
author: sparc
